description:
What I was trying to mint the day... Violent events happened 2 weeks ago. I couldn't get Beacon  to Synch. I'm safe, i'm back to art, I'm officially dismissed from militia duty and can focus on the arts much more.
   1 Edition for every person who helped save me not for sale, and 1 for everyone who cared that I was gone up for Swap.

This #RecappiCard grants players +14 to any 1d20 roll that critically fails.
